---
title: "docs: update PRDoc documentation, add .prdoc.toml config, and CI workflow"

doc:
  - audience: Framework Dev
    description: |
      Completes the PRDoc system migration by adopting the polkadot-sdk style
      skeleton approach. Removes all LLM infrastructure, rewrites the generator
      to use cargo_metadata for crate detection, updates the CLI with --bump
      and --audience parameters, adds backport branch validation, and creates
      Tera templates for per-audience changelog generation.

      Key changes:
      - Removed: llm.rs, local_llm.rs, embed.rs, summary.rs
      - Rewrote: generator.rs with polkadot-sdk style skeleton generation
      - Updated CLI: montrs agent prdoc generate --pr 82 --bump minor --audience app_dev
      - Added: validate_prdoc_for_branch() for backport major bump checks
      - Added: .prdoc.toml config file
      - Added: Tera templates for per-audience changelog
      - Updated CI workflows to remove LLM/Ollama references

crates: [ ]
---